  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Harvest <span class=\"name name-special\">Quad Servos</span> from the remains of <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinel Quads</span>, an advanced combat unit deployed at high alert levels.<br>Collect loot from defeated Sentinels by destroying <VAL_ON>Combat Supply Barrels<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从一台在高度警惕级别时部署的高级战斗单位<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫四足机甲</span>的残骸上，收集<span class=\"name name-special\">四足机甲伺服</span>。<br>通过摧毁<VAL_ON>战斗补给桶<>，从已击败的护卫身上收集战利品。",
    "TencentChinese": "从一台在高度警惕级别时部署的高级战斗单位<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫四足机甲</span>的残骸上，收集<span class=\"name name-special\">四足机甲伺服</span>。<br>通过破坏<VAL_ON>战斗补给桶<>，从已击败的护卫身上收集战利品。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從高度警惕級別時所部署的先進戰鬥機體<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警四足機甲</span>的殘骸上收集<span class=\"name name-special\">四足機甲伺服</span>。<br>從通過摧毀<VAL_ON>戰鬥補給桶<>擊敗的巡警身上收集戰利品。"
  },
